---
title: Sausage and Tomato Pesto Pasta with Pesto and Roasted Tenderstem®
description: Crispy roasted tenderstem® broccoli, a rich tomatoey ragu, fresh pesto and cheese are the winning combination in this simple wheat pasta recipe. Using our delicious pork and oregano sausage meat as the base of the ragu makes this recipe quick and easy to cook, ready in just 25 mins. Serve up in bowls and top with the remaining cheese and a spoonful of pesto for a fresh finish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tomatoey-pesto-pasta-ad4d0878-bd43fc2b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/tomatoey-pesto-pasta-5bebf7d530006c607f547902-67eaf9ed.pdf
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
author: Mimi Morley
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 970 kcal
  fat: 39 g
  saturated fat: 14 g
  carbohydrates: 106 g
  sugar: 17 g
  protein: 44 g
  sodium: 4 g
